These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, hot-chocolate
The people have 2 different jobs:  dancer, lawyer
There are 2 different nationalities: argentine, chinese
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, quad-bike
1. the lawyer is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
2. the dancer is on the right of the lawyer##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate      | juice    |
| Job           | lawyer | dancer |
| Nationality   | argentine       | chinese  |
| Transport     | helicopter      | quad-bike     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-2::.
There 2 different types of food: pomegranate, lime
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, trance
2 different pets are kept: goldfish, pony
The people use 2 different means of transport: train, jet-ski
1. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
2. the person eating lime is on the left of the fan of trance##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Food          | lime | pomegranate |
| Music-Genre   | disco       | trance         |
| Pet           | pony     | goldfish         |
| Transport     | jet-ski    | train    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: reading, chess
The people have 2 different jobs:  writer, dancer
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, ambient
The people use 2 different means of transport: taxi, boat
1. the fan of ambient is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the writer##1
3. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
4. the person driving the boat is on the left of the fan of ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |      2      |
| Hobby         | chess          | reading |
| Job           | dancer | writer     |
| Music-Genre   | punk            | ambient         |
| Transport     | boat         | taxi   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-4::.
