2. the person drinking water is the owner of the ferret##1
3. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| Beverage      | water     | fanta   |
| Movie-Genre   | animation    | documentary |
| Music-Genre   | funk   | soul |
| Pet           | ferret | lizard    |

