.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-20::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, sprite
There 2 different types of food: zucchini, kiwi
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: rock, techno
The people use 2 different means of transport: trike, helicopter
1. the fan of techno is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person eating zucchini is the fan of rock##1
3. the fan of rock is the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage      | sprite     | 7up |
| Food          | kiwi   | zucchini |
| Music-Genre   | techno     | rock     |
| Transport     | trike | helicopter     |

 